    <p class="section-number">06, Models we service most often</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Whirlpool models in heavy SoCal service rotation.</h2>

    <p class="lead">A representative sample of Whirlpool model families our techs service routinely. Whirlpool's catalog is broad and overlaps with Maytag and KitchenAid; the model groups below cover the units that show up most often on our route.</p>

    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card">
