        <p>Core Whirlpool refrigeration. WRF = French Door, WRS = Side-by-Side, WRX = Counter-Depth. 2018-2021 manufacture dates fall within wire-harness class action window.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Refrigerators, Top &amp; Bottom Freezer</h3>
        <p class="model-list">WRT318FZDW · WRT519SZDM · WRB322DMHV · WRB329DMBM</p>
        <p>Value-tier refrigeration in production-builder homes. WRT = top-freezer, WRB = bottom-freezer. Standard service tree, less class-action exposure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Washers, Cabrio Top-Load</h3>
        <p class="model-list">WTW8500DW · WTW7000DW · WTW6120HW · WTW5000DW · WTW4855HW</p>
        <p>Cabrio HE top-load family. Lid lock and suspension rod dominate service mix. Reliable workhorses through year 10-12 with normal maintenance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Washers, Duet Front-Load</h3>
        <p class="model-list">WFW8620HC · WFW862CHC · WFW9620HC · WFW5605MW · WFW6605MW</p>
        <p>Duet front-load family. CCU board, drain pump, door boot, and bearing dominate service tree. Year 8-12 bearing service typical.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
